<% content_for :title, "Cookie Policy - Fantasy Forecast" %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
      Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
    </p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Are Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit our website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide information to website owners.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Fantasy Forecast uses cookies to enhance your experience on our FPL consensus ranking platform. We use cookies for:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>Keeping you signed in to your forecaster account</li>
        <li>Remembering your preferences and settings</li>
        <li>Analyzing website traffic and user behavior</li>
        <li>Improving our FPL ranking algorithms and user experience</li>
        <li>Providing security features and preventing fraud</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibred text-gray-900 mb-4">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Essential Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They include cookies that allow you to be remembered as you explore the site within a single session or from session to session.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Performance Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        These cookies collect information about how you use our website, such as which pages you visit most often. This data helps us optimize our FPL ranking service and improve user experience.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Functional Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        These cookies allow our website to remember choices you make (such as your username or language preference) and provide enhanced, more personal features.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Analytics Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We use analytics cookies to understand how visitors interact with our website. This helps us improve our FPL consensus rankings and forecaster features.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We may also use third-party cookies from trusted partners to help us analyze website usage and improve our services. These may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>Google Analytics for website analytics</li>
        <li>Social media platforms for content sharing</li>
        <li>Authentication services for secure login</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        You have the right to decide whether to accept or reject cookies. You can exercise your cookie preferences by:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>Modifying your browser settings to control cookie usage</li>
        <li>Deleting existing cookies from your browser</li>
        <li>Using private/incognito browsing mode</li>
        <li>Opting out of analytics tracking</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Please note that disabling cookies may affect your ability to use certain features of our FPL ranking platform.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cookie Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        The length of time cookies remain on your device depends on their type:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
        <li><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain until they expire or you delete them</li>
        <li><strong>Authentication Cookies:</strong> Usually last for the duration of your login session</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in technology, legislation, or our business practices. Please check this page periodically for updates.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Email: privacy@fantasyforecast.com<br>
        Address: [Your Business Address]
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>